Titolo: Home Alone 2: Lost in New York (video game)

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: Home Alone 2: Lost in New York is a 1992 video game based loosely on the 1992 film of the same name; it was released on the Nintendo Entertainment System, Genesis, Game Boy, DOS and Super NES platforms. It was dedicated to Tom D. Heidt, a programmer who died shortly before it was released.